00:59:49,200 --> 00:59:51,440
I ove godine, 2020.

728
00:59:51,520 --> 00:59:54,720
godine, prikupili smo 481.000 dolara u pandemiji.

729
00:59:55,040 --> 00:59:55,440
Banane.

