01:00:28,080 --> 01:00:28,960
To je poruka, zar ne?

741
01:00:29,280 --> 01:00:30,160
Želim se skloniti.

742
01:00:30,480 --> 01:00:34,000
Samo želim podijeliti njihovu poruku, zar ne?

